description:
A simple notebook with an attractive cover in which to write down and store all your favorite recipes and thus create your own personal recipe book to keep close at hand.

 It contains 100 cream-colored pages to fill with 100 fabulous recipes in which to report for each of them:

 the TITLE of the recipe;
 CATEGORY e.g. first course, second course, dessert;
 the INGREDIENTS used;
 the PROCEDURE;
 PREPARATION TIME;
 the COOKING TIME;
 the PORTIONS for which it is made;
 final NOTES to note any other useful information.
 All enriched by nice illustrations.

 The format is practical and convenient, not too small nor too large so that it can be used with ease: 6 x 9 inches / 15.2 cm x 22.8 cm.
